graph TB
    subgraph "Notebook Controller Component"
        Controller[NotebookReconciler<br/>Main Controller]
        Culler[CullingReconciler<br/>Idle Notebook Culling]
        Metrics[Metrics Collector<br/>Prometheus Exporter]

        Controller -->|monitors activity| Culler
        Controller -->|emits metrics| Metrics
        Culler -->|emits metrics| Metrics
    end

    subgraph "Generated Resources"
        StatefulSet[StatefulSet<br/>Notebook Pod]
        Service[ClusterIP Service<br/>Port 80→8888]
        VirtualService[Istio VirtualService<br/>External Routing]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        NotebookCRv1[Notebook CR v1<br/>Storage Version]
        NotebookCRv1beta1[Notebook CR v1beta1<br/>Webhook Support]
        NotebookCRv1alpha1[Notebook CR v1alpha1<br/>Legacy]

        NotebookCRv1beta1 -.->|converts to| NotebookCRv1
        NotebookCRv1alpha1 -.->|converts to| NotebookCRv1
    end

    User[User/Admin] -->|creates| NotebookCRv1
    NotebookCRv1 -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/updates| StatefulSet
    Controller -->|creates| Service
    Controller -->|creates when USE_ISTIO=true| VirtualService

    StatefulSet -->|manages| Pod[Notebook Pod<br/>Jupyter Server<br/>Port 8888]
    Service -->|routes to| Pod
    VirtualService -->|routes via| Gateway[Istio Gateway<br/>kubeflow/kubeflow-gateway]
    Gateway -->|forwards to| Service

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraping]
        IstioMesh[Istio Service Mesh<br/>mTLS]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/manages resources| K8sAPI
    Culler -->|checks /api/kernels| Pod
    Culler -->|updates annotations| K8sAPI
    Metrics -->|scraped by| Prometheus
    VirtualService -.->|configured via| IstioMesh

    subgraph "Configuration"
        ConfigMap1[ConfigMap: config<br/>USE_ISTIO, ISTIO_GATEWAY, ADD_FSGROUP]
        ConfigMap2[ConfigMap: notebook-controller-culler-config<br/>ENABLE_CULLING, CULL_IDLE_TIME]
    end

    Controller -->|reads| ConfigMap1
    Culler -->|reads| ConfigMap2

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Culler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Metrics fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCRv1 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCRv1beta1 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style NotebookCRv1alpha1 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style StatefulSet fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Service fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style VirtualService fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style IstioMesh fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
